revision.text:
'''Artstein's theorem''' states that a [[dynamical system]] has a differentiable [[control-Lyapunov function]] if and only if there exists a regular stabilizing feedback: <math>u(x)</math>.<ref>Sontag, Eduardo D. [http://citeseer.ist.psu.edu/sontag89universal.html A Universal Construction Of Artstein's Theorem On Nonlinear Stabilization]</ref>
